lcn to Putney Bridge, but couldn't decide whether the sign was to Bagley or Pearscroft

tags.description:
I believe the purpose of this dropped kerb, with the shared space directly to the north is to facilitate joining Eel Brook Common for northbound cyclists from WBR. 
Southbound, joining WBR is possible, but hairy. (use ASL but beware of left-filter)
